  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>お前らか。
いろんな奴にケンカ吹っかけて
トラブル起こしまくってるってのは</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So it's you guys. The ones who keep popping up
picking all kinds of fights and causing tons of trouble.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なに言ってるんだよ？
おれはみんなの為に戦ってんだぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What're you talking about?
I'm fighting for the good of everyone!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>自覚なし、か。
こりゃタチが悪いぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Non-existent self-awareness, huh.
Those sorts are all kinds of bad.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>一回痛い目見ないと
わからねぇんだろうな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're not gonna get it unless you
get whacked around at least once, huh.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……そうだな。　お前の言う通りだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...You're right. It's exactly as you say it is.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
